00:35:43.920 --> 00:35:48.980
lead to social capabilities of
a certain kind, whereas early

00:35:48.980 --> 00:35:52.440
childhood neglect seems to lead
to social disabilities.

00:35:52.440 --> 00:35:56.630
In making that statement, A, I
